{"tid":1509291,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"養隻鼠真係一波三折 2","createTime":"2019-08-26T19:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T02:13:42.000Z","uid":209799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e46d316144923fd7d1ba57c98e7461e39354feef","tid":1509291,"uid":209799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你隻鼠會冇事的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw 起完樓主底 你隻仔真係孱弱的寶寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>過左身。。。<br />\n<br />\n有好多好多野想講 真係有好多好多野想講<br />\n<br />\n太多<br />\n講唔岀口<br />\n<br />\n有三大樣野想講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1</span><br />\n<br />\n本人在此  多謝咁多位巴絲打幫助我<br />\n<br />\n無論係過往 or 財仔今晚(我隻鼠叫財<br />\n<br />\n多謝你地比唔同既建議我<br />\n<br />\n財仔係天堂上會多謝哥哥姐姐<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2</span><br />\n<br />\n在此想多謝我女朋友同屋企人<br />\n<br />\n佢勸說我養財仔<br />\n<br />\n教導我<br />\n<br />\n屋企人雖然口硬話放佢出街<br />\n<br />\n但都係我去旅行時照顧佢<br />\n<br />\n需要屋企人好on9 比d 落左鹽炒蛋財仔<br />\n<br />\n但都係基於愛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3</span><br />\n<br />\n多謝財仔<br />\n<br />\n比個機會我照顧你<br />\n<br />\n係你臨終時 你都張大眼望住我<br />\n<br />\n平時就算咬我也不痛<br />\n<br />\n係哥哥對你唔住<br />\n<br />\n冇再細心d<br />\n<br />\n係哥哥冇錢<br />\n<br />\n我應該帶你去24小時醫院睇<br />\n<br />\n但我冇能力<br />\n<br />\n係我虧欠左你 但都好多謝你呢1個月入面既陪伴<br />\n<br />\n我全家都因為你多左好多歡樂<br />\n<br />\n再見了<br />\n你好鐘意跑步 仲要跑好快<br />\n<br />\n希望會跑到上天堂<br />\n一定會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c4vrwrQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4vrwrQ.png&h=212ad841&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BehNfTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBehNfTx.jpg&h=c02728be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4185d480c53696ac251c3f42cb8317055106a54","tid":1509291,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl